#                 Terkel Gjervig Hansen (prompts / kleur),
#                 Einar Otto Stangvik / Luigi Pinca
#                 (websockets/ws), James Long / Mozilla
#                 (nunjucks).  Rebecca's iarna ecosystem
#                 emphasizes npm-internals infrastructure
#                 + lightweight zero-dep utilities.)
